com.googlecode.tesseract.android

Class ResultIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.tesseract.android.PageIterator
      • com.googlecode.tesseract.android.ResultIterator

  • public class ResultIterator
extends PageIterator
    Java interface for the ResultIterator. Does not implement all available JNI methods, but does implement enough to be useful. Comments are adapted from original Tesseract source.
    Author:
    alanv@google.com (Alan Viverette)

      • confidence

        public float confidence(int level)
        Returns the mean confidence of the current object at the given level. The number should be interpreted as a percent probability (0-100).
        Parameters:
        level - the page iterator level. See TessBaseAPI.PageIteratorLevel.

      • getChoicesAndConfidence

        public java.util.List<<any>> getChoicesAndConfidence(int level)
        Returns all possible matching text strings and their confidence level for the current object at the given level.

        The default matching text is blank (""). The default confidence level is zero (0.0)

        Parameters:
        level - the page iterator level. See TessBaseAPI.PageIteratorLevel.
        Returns:
        A list of pairs with the UTF string and the confidence
